WEBVTT

00:10:27.948 --> 00:10:31.575
the German philosopher who wrote
a book called "The Human Condition."

00:10:32.170 --> 00:10:35.609
And in it, she says that classically,

00:10:35.633 --> 00:10:38.299
work is associated with men.

00:10:38.323 --> 00:10:40.533
Work is what comes out of the head;

00:10:40.557 --> 00:10:41.833
it's what we invent,

00:10:41.857 --> 00:10:43.388
it's what we create,

00:10:43.412 --> 00:10:46.052
it's how we leave our mark upon the world.

00:10:47.434 --> 00:10:51.876
Whereas labor is associated with the body.

00:10:51.900 --> 00:10:54.691
It's associated with the people
who perform labor

00:10:54.715 --> 00:10:56.343
or undergo labor.

00:10:56.915 --> 00:10:59.638
So to me,

00:10:59.662 --> 00:11:03.790
the mindset that denies that,